" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Gross pathology of an intralobar pulmonary sequestration (ILS)",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 263px; height: 388px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    A large distended systemic artery is present at one border (red arrow). A dilated, mucus filled bronchus (blue arrow) is evident adjacent to the artery. The lung parenchyma has a microcystic appearance, distinguishing it from the adjacent normal parenchyma.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
